title: John Fitzgerald Kennedy National Historic Site: History & Culture
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     History & Culture             History & Culture       Looking to learn more about the Kennedy family and important stories within their lives? These pages will help you. Travel back in time and explore the neighborhood the Kennedys called home in Brookline. Learn more about the family and discover some of their stories. Curious about objects on display in the home? Our curator's blog or our collections page will introduce you to these items.
